Package org.oucs.oxpoints.entities.pool Description

OxPointsEntityPools are collections of OxPointsEntitys. OxPointsEntityPools can be generated automatically from OxPointsSnapshots or Jena Models.

An OxPointsEntityPool can be seen as the internal representation of a snapshot of RDF. OxPointsEntityPools can be transformed into RDF or other output formats such as KML.

For most queries to the OxPoints system an OxPointsEntityPool is created that is then transformed into the demanded output format.
